ITALIAN HOT CHOCOLATE ☕️🍫 A hot chocolate recipe to cosy yourself up! thick, smooth and creamy hot drink that takes only less than 10 minutes to make 😋 RECIPE (2-3 servings) 𝑰𝒏𝒈𝒓𝒆𝒅𝒊𝒆𝒏𝒕𝒔 * 1 1/2 cup whole milk (350 ml), Divided * 1 tbsp (8 g) Corn starch/corn flour * 1 tbsp (6 g) Unsweetened Cocoa powder * A pinch of salt * 1/4 tsp vanilla extract * 80g Chocolate(40g dark chocolate (54%) + 40g milk chocolate), Approximately 1/2 cup + 1 tbsp of total chocolate) * 2 tbsp - 2 1/2 tbsp Sugar (25g - 31g) * 125 ml (1/2 cup) Whipping cream, cold * 1 tbsp icing sugar * Chocolate shavings 𝑫𝒊𝒓𝒆𝒄𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏𝒔 1. In a chilled bowl, whip cold whipping cream + icing sugar together until stiff peaks form. Cover and keep in the fridge. 2. Chop both of the chocolates into small pieces. Set aside. 3. In a small bowl, mix 1 tbsp corn starch and 1/4 cup of milk, set aside. 4. In a small saucepan, add 1 1/4 cup milk + sifted cocoa powder + sugar and whisk together. (I added 2 tbsp sugar here, you can add more if you want the chocolate sweeter). 5. Heat the mixture over medium-low heat, whisking often to avoid lumps. Bring the mixture to a simmer, reduce the heat and add the corn flour mixture, whisk continuously until well combined and drink has thickened(for about 2-3 minutes). 6. Add a pinch of salt + vanilla extract (optional) 7. Turn off the heat and stir in the chopped chocolate,whisk it until the chocolate is completely dissolved and you get a smooth, silky and thick hot chocolate. 8. Pour into a mug, add whipped cream on top and garnish with chocolate shavings. Enjoy! ☕️🤎 #hotchocolate #italianhotchocolate #hotchocolatetime #christmas #holidayseason

🥔 Accordion Potatoes 📝 Recipe 1-2 Potato Water 1 tsp • Salt 1 tsp • Baking Soda Oil Dried Parsley Chili Sauce Steps: • Cutting the Potato - Peel off the potato - Cut the ends of potato - Cut the potato lengthwise / just like shown in my video, however you like and based on the size of the potato - Take 2 skewers - Put the potato horizontally and place the skewers on both sides of the potato - Cut the potato in vertical lines - Flip the potato - Cut the potato again in diagonal lines • Soaking; Accordion Potatoes - Prepare water with salt and baking soda - Soak the accordion potatoes in water for 5-10 minutes - After soaking the potatoes, dry them with tissue / towel • Cooking; Accordion Potatoes - Heat the oil in pan at medium heat - Fry the accordion potatoes until crispy and golden brown • Finishing; Accordion Potatoes - Serve the potato with dried parsley and chili sauce Tips: 1. After cutting the potato into accordion shape, you will slice another ones. So keep the potato that have already been cut in water to prevent the potato turning into brown color. Recipe inspired by: @hildansl Notice a different hand in the frame? My friend had a sleepover in my place, so I invited her to make this recipe with me 🤣 thank you, friend 😉 By the way it was a lot of work to make this recipe but I had a lot of fun, I love the shape 🪗 it’s so unique, and it turned out really delicious and crispy! 😍🤤🤤 #accordionpotatoes #potato #fries #potatoes #homecafe #홈카페 #asmr #homecooking #homecook #cooking #cookingathome #onthetable

Efforts to boost exports encompass the implementation of enticing incentives for start-ups and new exporters, alongside streamlining compliance norms for existing exporters. One notable example is the revamped Market Access Initiatives (MAI) Scheme, which now provides airfare reimbursement for new exporters and start-ups participating in overseas events. The primary goal of this initiative is to encourage emerging export players from India to venture into the global market and showcase their products or services internationally. Unlike before, entities with an annual turnover of Rs. 50 Lakh are now eligible for the MAI scheme's incentives. Qualified companies stand to receive airfare assistance up to Rs. 75,000 (Rs. 1 lakh for LAC and North America) or the cost of the ticket, whichever is lower. Objectives of the Market Access Initiative scheme: In addition to its pivotal role in promoting the export of products and services, the initiative provides support to micro, small, and medium enterprises to: 1 Expand their businesses into new export markets. 2 Embrace innovation and technology. 3 Acquire knowledge about trade and export. 4 Develop and acquire essential skill sets. 5 Understand the interventions necessary to enter new international markets. To avail the benefits of the MAI, membership in any of the 14 export promotion councils under the administrative control of the Department of Commerce is required. These councils include EEPC India, PEPC, Chemexcil, CAPEXIL, Council for Leather Exports, Sports Goods Export Promotion Council, Gem and Jewellery Export Promotion Council, Shellac Export Promotion Council, Cashew Export Promotion Council of India, The Plastics Export Promotion Council, EPCES, Pharmaceutical Export Promotion Council, IOPEPC, and Services Export Promotion Council. . . . It will be integrated across Google's products like search, ads, and the Bard chatbot. Gemini comes in three versions: Gemini Ultra, Gemini Pro, and Gemini Nano. Gemini is now available in Bard for English, in over 170 countries. Gemini Nano will power Pixel 8 smartphones' messaging replies, while Gemini Pro will be accessible to developers via Google Cloud's API from December 13. Gemini Ultra, the most powerful version, is set to debut in 2024, with availability in Bard Advanced next year. Gemini can analyze pictures, answer questions, create images from text, understand math problems, and update charts with new data. The launch of Gemini is a significant AI milestone for Google, expected to enhance user experience in its products and services. Which means- 1. Kids carry forward their MOTHER’s names 2. Men move into their Wives’ homes 3. Property belongs to the women, enabling a sense of SECURITY 4. There is NO Dowry 5. "The Golden Ratio being Irrational" Here's a trance edit of my previous post with 300k frames in 60 Seconds! Made with python , matplotlib . Post editing on Adobe After Effects Explanation : The graph is visualized on complex plane, Here is the function : z(θ)=e^θi + e^Φθi θ = Angle made by the Inner Arm e = Euler's constant i = Imaginary number The first half of the equation e^θi represents the inner arm and second half of the equation represents the outer arm. This simulation animates the angle θ from 0 to approximately 150000 degrees. The visual illustrates a setup where the outer arm is rotating golden ratio times faster than the inner arm. Since the golden ratio is an irrational number with infinite digits, the line would never connect to its starting Position, no matter how long, how fast we run this simulation. If you zoom in you'd always see the gap between those lines. Hence it fills every possible space enclosed within a circle. #mathematics #geometry #pattern #sacredgeometry #goldenratio #adhd #ocd #spirograph #trance #math #edit #oddlysatisfying #satisfying #unsatisfying #profound #transcendent #surreal #interesting #mindblowing
